==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: feed bag
<hw>feed bag</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a
canvas bag that is used to feed an animal (such as a horse or mule);
animal feed such as oats are placed in the bag, and it is fastened at
the top of the head, covering the muzzle. The animal may then eat the
contents while thus wearing the feedbag.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nosebag.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Feeder</ent>⟦br⟧
